title: I’m Not a Good Web Developer, I’m Just Good at Googling Things
excerpt: Dev diaries is a development community providing daily tips and tricks about web development. Learn about how to become a better dev, and get a refreshed perspective on what it means to be a web developer. We share daily web development tips on Instagram, Twitter, Facebook, & Pinterest.  Being a good web developer comes down to a lot of things, but one of the major skills is being able to Google and find the right answer on Stackoverflow...
